\c 39
\s Nhume dzinobva Bhabhironi
\s dzinoshanyira Hezekia
\p
\v 3 oi
\v 1 Zvino nenguva iyo Merodhaki
\s bharadhani mwanakomana wa
\s Bharadhani, mambo weBhabhironi, aka
\s tuma tsamba nechipo kuna Hezekia;
\s nokuti akanga anzwa kuti airwara akapo
\p razve.
\v 2 Hezekia akafara pamusoro pavo,
\s akavaratidza imba yakanga ine zvinoko
\s s\la zvake, sirivha, nendarama, nezvinonhuwira, namafuta anokosha, neimba yaiva nenhumbi dzake dzose dzokurwa nadzo, nezvose zvakanga zviri papfuma yake; kwakanga kusisina chinhu mumba
\p make, kana muushe hwake hwose, chavasina kuratidzwa naHezekia.
\v 3 Zvino muporofita Isaya akasvika kuna mambo Hezekia, akati kwaari, "Varume ava vakati kudiniko? Vakasvika kwauri vachibvepi?" Hezekia akati, "Vakanga vabva kunyika iri kure, Bhabhironi vachiuya kwandiri."
\p
\v 4 Ipapo akati, "Vakaonei mumba mako?" Hezekia akapindura, akati, "Vakaona zvose zviri mumba mangu; hakune chinhu pakati pepfuma yangu chandisina kuvaratidza."
\p
\v 5 Ipapo Isaya akati kuna Hezekia, "Inzwa shoko raJehovha wehondo,
\v 6 â€˜Tarira, mazuva achasvika, nenguva iyo zvose zviri mumba mako, nezvose zvakaunganidzwa namadzibaba ako kusvikira zuva ranhasi, zvichaiswa Bhabhironi, hakuna chinhu chichasiyiwa,' ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 7 Vamwe vanakomana vako, vachabva kwauri, vauchabereka, vachatapwa; vachava varanda mumba mamambo weBhabhironi."
\p
\v 8 Ipapo Hezekia akati kuna Isaya, "Shoko raJehovha ramataura rakanaka haro." Akatiwo, "Nokuti rugare nezvokwadi zvichavapo pamazuva angu."
